column5: Hey guys, I was fishing a creek in Oshawa today and lost a pair of my Maui Jim glasses. I just bought these glasses and they cost me and arm and a leg so if anyone has seen them or finds them can you please let me know. Saw a few guys down there so hopefully someone find them and returns them. Thanks guys.   -Fishnpro
I'll keep my eyes open for them. Any luck out there today?  Dirk....

Well look at it this way...at least you didn't lose them down a port-o-potty  Saw a nice pair sitting on "top" of the pile a couple weeks ago in Trenton.  Man that would suck.  Hope you find yours in a clean condition
No to much slush on the creeks.....its been ok in the afternoons
